    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Capacity building of cooperatives s & factories on organic practice & standards        \r\n    Support Agro-vets companies and cooperatives to get engaged in organic input supply to farmers. \r\n    Facilitate the establishment of credit lines with factories and cooperatives \r\n    Facilitate the cooperatives to establish green leaf collection centres \r\n    IB brokering between anchor companies and their cooperatives \r\n    Capacity development of district level cooperative federations and a central federation for lobbying and advocacy.  \r\n    Facilitate Public Private Dialogue concerning the existing tea policy \r\n    Technical Assistance to Ministry of Agriculture and Commerce to develop Organic Agriculture policy"
    },
